divs: Sighting DetailsGuess what- I was coming from market and was eating ice-cream and as soon I look up at sky- high there was something shining- First with led rights..and then that body divided in two parts and started giving white lights. I bet check on the news tomorrow..It was Un-Identified flying object...UFO...Another life exist in this universe this claim is enough to support that... whooooo am luckier one.. I tried to call up police but network failure showed up and did not dialed up...time was I guess around 9:30 pm [India timings]...there were tooo much stars so i could not keep track on it for long time... that was not plane, helicopter or satellite ..that was something else...I can love aliens instead of humans.. ha ha..its so fascinating...come on news channels and NASA pick up the matter
